body:
### expected behaviour
uploading animation icon should change into file type icon after uploading finishes. browser should know that there is no operation in progress (e.g. chrome asks if i am sure to leave the page even uploading is already finished behind the scenes.

### actual behaviour
animation doesn't stop, it seems that uploading never finishes but in reality upload is already finished.

### steps to reproduce
1. download oc 5.0.2
2. install it into iis+php or xampp
3. upload any kind of file, any size.

### server configuration
operating system: windows server 2008 r2

web server: iis/apache (tested with both)

database: sqlite

php version: 5.4

owncloud version: 5.0.2

### client configuration
browser: chromium (several versions), ie 9

operating system: win 2008 r2, win 7

